name: Nite Ize SlideLock Aluminum Carabiner
description: This light accessory carabiner improves on the traditional design, with flat cross-section (instead of tubular) profile. It's easy to feed through small openings.Solid aluminum construction is lightweight and strong.Stainless steel gate with slide-to-lock mechanism that locks the gate with a quick push and slide movement.Weight rating for Size #2: 4.5kg.Weight rating for Size #4: 34kg.Not for use where disengagement could result in bodily injury or property damage.Not for climbing.
